 The UI of the app consists of the following elements:

- A menu bar with the following items:
    - Merlin Project Express
    - File
    - Edit
    - View
    - Insert
    - Format
    - Tools
    - Window
    - Help
- A toolbar with the following buttons:
    - New Document
    - Open Document
    - Save Document
    - Print Document
    - Cut
    - Copy
    - Paste
    - Undo
    - Redo
- A sidebar with the following sections:
    - Recent Documents
    - Help & Instructions
    - Templates
- A main area that displays the current document.
- A status bar that displays information about the current document.